<br>
My 2hs and 1hs are at 200 now (for a few levels more) and 1hb and 2hp are very close. I was using a ghoulbane from back when they were droppable (now it sits in a bag unless I need to have a shield for bashing, and when I buy better, it becomes bankware). 2hb is under 100.<br>
<br>
2hp: Messengers of the Queen are under 100p and are frequently gifts to newbies on my server. Folks want the centi war spear.<br>
<br>
1hb: practice it some, you *may* come across a wonderful 1hb, the one I use is from Kithicor and has only 1 remarkable feature: +6 wis (otherwise it is basically no-drop FS junk)<br>
<br>
The 2hb I drag around with me to practice while LFG is a glowing wooden crook (real cheap junk off of lockjaw, but has the remarkable feature of being paladin usable, most affordable 2hb are not). If I can obtain the no drop 2hb from ME, then I will spend a LOT more time practicing 2hb. <p><a href='http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=64195'>Combat Profile</a><br>
<a href='http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=64207'>Tradeskill Profile</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ubizomb.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Bizomb</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 869<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(3/27/02 9:06:15 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=317.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: If could only train in 2 melee skills, which.....</span><hr size=1> yeah, I was gonna say 2hs and 2hb. Or 2hs and 2hp.<br>
I went 2hs and 1hs route basically tho when I grew up pallies couldn't pierce so that wasn't really an option anyway and 2hblunt weapons were few and far between. Now there are alot of innexpensive or easily camped 2 hand blunts and piercers that are really good weapons.<br>
<br>
I'd suggest you try to keep em all maxed, but 2hs and 2hp or 2hb are probably your best bets. That centi spear at 20/30 is really nice and they are pretty common and cheap.<br>
