<br>
1hs Shadow Flame Long Sword (12/26, +3 Fire Dmg, +8 STR, +5 AGI, +3 CHA, +4 STA, +50 HP, +10 mana, +10 sv Fire)<br>
<br>
2hs Strength of Grodan (41/51, +25 STR, +10 STA)<br>
<br>
2hb Petrified Rod (39/44, +5 All Stats, +50 HP, +50 mana, +10 sv all)<br>
<br>
1hb Goranga Spiked Club (12/23, +5 AC, +2 STR)<br>
<br>
2hp Etched Velium War Lance (30/35)<br>
<br>
All these are kept in a Rallic bag on me at all times. Depending on my roll in the group dictates what weapon load-out I use. You never know what weapon is gonna drop and you don't want to be caught short on any skill IMHO. <br>
